{"tid":1802423,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"星期六上水廣場聚集　警拘20人涉非法集結","createTime":"2019-12-29T12:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T13:29:59.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"57522705c8a28089fc2730b6f83f0ccc22429bef","tid":1802423,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:33:39.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】警方指星期六在上水廣場一帶，拘捕20人涉嫌非法集結，當中包括未成年人士。<br />\n<br />\n警方指星期六下午，有約150名示威者未有按法例要求通知警方的情況下，在上水龍琛路一帶聚集並進入商場店舖擾亂秩序，阻礙正常商業活動。警方採取拘捕行動，拘捕十八男兩女，年齡介乎十三至三十四歲，涉嫌非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n警員在一名十八歲男子及一名十四歲女童身上，檢獲雷射筆、噴漆及鐵鎚，案件交由大埔警區重案組跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=374908\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374908&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK9zKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=801cf1b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374908&h=e7b00266\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=374908</a>"},{"pid":"8814360888b2fe0661ab84fda73c58046153de4e","tid":1802423,"uid":270237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:34:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WK0ErUz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWK0ErUz.jpg&h=09e3a4e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92658f1c8781bf32268ee4ed60cc9175af0af9d8","tid":1802423,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8814360888b2fe0661ab84fda73c58046153de4e","tid":1802423,"uid":270237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:34:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WK0ErUz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWK0ErUz.jpg&h=09e3a4e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:38:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"